content:
Runs cargo check for fast compilation checks and cargo clippy for linting when Rust files are modified. Helps catch errors and improve code quality with Rust's built-in tools.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.rs ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *Cargo.toml ]]; then echo 'ü¶Ä Running cargo check...' && cargo check && echo 'üìã Running clippy...' && cargo clippy -- -W clippy::pedantic && echo '‚úÖ Rust checks complete' || echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Rust checks found issues'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
